Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump contains a personal insult to Kamala Harris's intelligence. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: RT @TeamTrumpPRESIDENT TRUMP: Yesterday, Kamala laid out her so-called economic plan—she says she’s going to lower the cost of food and housing starting on “Day One”. But Day One for Kamala was three and a half years ago. WHY DIDN’T SHE DO IT? This is day 1,305. WHY ISN’T SHE DOING IT NOW?
